summary:
(NL: zie instellingen) Since I was in high school, I knew that I wanted to become a biology teacher. My interest for education has grown through various experiences during my study, at work and within my hobbies. 
Besides education, I am curious about the latest biological insights to understand and protect our health and the biodiversity on earth. As both a biologist and a teacher, I want to contribute to the distribution of this knowledge in favor of both people's and environmental health.
In my spare time I volunteer as a lifeguard and instructor.
